# Sidecar files generated by matrix tests when the admin opens the
# Publish panel against this fixture's editable target. The source-side
# sidecar writer backfills `.<8-hex>.hash`, `.uses-*`, and `.tpl-*`
# files under targets/local-edit/ on first compare. They're transient
# test state — regenerated every run, never authoritative — so we
# ignore the patterns rather than commit a snapshot.
#
# Pattern reference: docs/sidecars.md (the three sidecar kinds).
**/.[0-9a-f][0-9a-f][0-9a-f][0-9a-f][0-9a-f][0-9a-f][0-9a-f][0-9a-f].hash
**/.uses-*
**/.tpl-*
